data.description: Beautifully renovated four bedrooms, three full bath Fells Point townhome with 2,665 sqft of liveable space & 3,510sqft total! With a walk score of 98, it's a walkers paradise - Walk to the best bars, restaurants & grocery stores within minutes! Enjoy a spacious living room and a chef's kitchen with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, wall oven/microwave, hooded gas range, tile back-splash,  soft close drawers, tile floor, breakfast bar, and a well-thought-out layout that flows into a dining area and opens to a private outdoor rear patio with dozens of plants that stay. This house has large rooms and an expansive center of the house around the staircase on all levels that open up the space and make it feel even more significant than it is. Hardwood floors, surround sound, dual zone HVAC,  skylights, and a rooftop deck with amazing panoramic views. This home has plenty of closet space and basement storage. All new construction in 2006. Whole home sound with amplifier. Cat5 Internet is wired to all rooms with a gigabyte switch in the basement. Schlage WiFi door lock. Multi-zone alarm. Ecobee thermostats. Included with the sale: back patio shed, rear patio drip system, main bedroom curtains, all blinds, floating shelves in bathroom number 2, TV in the kitchen,  all TV mounts & the washer /dryer. This house checks off all the boxes with Fells Point location and features!
